          .text Even when she's going formal, the NYLON girl wants to be an individual and have fun - she wants to have options, mix & match, make her own decisions. These separates capture her taste: colour blocking, cool neoprene fabric, ruffle & sheer details, and, of course, a healthy shot of NYLON pink.
          .author
            em Dani Stahl,
